15. Loyalty Stamps

a. Members of the Site have the opportunity to collect loyalty stamps when ordering from <%= company_name %> (indicated by the presence of a special icon). 

b. A loyalty stamp is earnt when an order is placed with <%= company_name %> on the Site and the order is Accepted and filled by <%= company_name %>.

c. You may earn a maximum of 1 stamp per day. Once you have collected a total of 5 or more stamps, you are able to exchange them for a 50% discount on your next order from <%= company_name %>. Please note that whilst you can earn stamps on any day of the week that you order, they can only be redeemed Monday - Thursday. 

d. Rates of discount may change without notice, and the offer may be withdrawn either from <%= company_name %> or from the whole of the Site without prior notice and with immediate effect. In such circumstances, any discounts due and stamps collected will be void, and neither <%= company_name %> nor IDDQD Limited may be held liable for any losses incurred as a result. 

e. Stamps have no cash value. The offer is non-exchangeable, and may only be used as described in these Terms of Use.

